---
const testimonials = [
  {
    quote:
      "I was so nervous about my wedding day, but Uzma's studio was like a sanctuary. She understood exactly what I wanted for my mehndi look — gold and burgundy, with intricate henna patterns that matched my wedding jewellery perfectly. Her team kept me calm, laughed with me, and made me feel like a bride should feel — absolutely radiant.",
    name: "Amna K.",
    event: "Bride · Bahria Town · 2024",
  },
  {
    quote:
      "My sister got married through SolaSinghar three years ago, so when it came time for my wedding, there was no question. Uzma delivered the same flawless bridal makeup I'd seen on my sister, and added her signature burgundy-gold extension work. My photos are absolutely magazine-ready. She's the only one I'd trust with my big day.",
    name: "Zara Q.",
    event: "Bride · Police Colony · 2024",
  },
  {
    quote:
      "Everyone at my reception kept asking who did my mehndi — the designs were so intricate and the gold accents just glowed under the studio lights at my walima. Uzma has this gift of understanding desi bridal traditions while making everything feel modern and editorial. I've already recommended her to six of my cousins in Rawalpindi.",
    name: "Mahnoor H.",
    event: "Bride · Kallay Syedan · 2023",
  },
  {
    quote:
      "For my engagement in Haraka, I booked Uzma for makeup and hair, and she created two completely different, equally stunning looks. The consistency and artistry across both occasions was unmatched. She's not just a makeup artist — she's a storyteller who makes every bride feel like the star of her own film.",
    name: "Nida M.",
    event: "Bride · Haraka · 2024",
  },
];
---

<section
  id="testimonials"
  class="relative py-24 md:py-32 lg:py-40"
  style="background-color: #0D0A07;"
>
  <!-- Top gold border -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 inset-x-0 h-px" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #D4AF37, transparent); opacity: 0.45;" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <!-- Top ornament -->
  <div class="flex justify-center mb-12">
    <svg width="60" height="20" viewBox="0 0 60 20" fill="none" stroke="#D4AF37" stroke-width="0.8" aria-hidden="true">
      <line x1="0" y1="10" x2="22" y2="10"/>
      <circle cx="30" cy="10" r="4"/>
      <circle cx="30" cy="10" r="1.5" fill="var(--color-gold)"/>
      <line x1="38" y1="10" x2="60" y2="10"/>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
    <!-- Heading -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 md:mb-20 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p class="eyebrow mb-6" style="color: #D4AF37;">
        Bride Stories
      </p>
      <h2 class="section-heading" style="color: #FAF6F0;">
        In the words of <em style="color: #D4AF37;">our brides.</em>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Quote grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 md:gap-8">
      {testimonials.map((t) => (
        <figure
          class="relative p-8 md:p-10 border flex flex-col h-full transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-[0_30px_60px_-20px_rgba(123,28,42,0.18)]"
          style="background-color: rgba(250,246,240,0.04); border-color: rgba(212,175,55,0.2);"
        >
          <!-- Decorative quote glyph -->
          <div
            class="absolute top-4 right-6 text-7xl leading-none opacity-25"
            style="font-family: var(--font-heading); color: rgba(212,175,55,0.15);"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            &ldquo;
          </div>

          <!-- Star row -->
          <div class="flex gap-1 mb-6 relative z-10" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars">
            {Array.from({ length: 5 }).map(() => (
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--color-gold)" aria-hidden="true">
                <polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/>
              </svg>
            ))}
          </div>

          <blockquote
            class="text-base md:text-[1.05rem] leading-relaxed flex-1 relative z-10"
            style="font-family: var(--font-heading); color: rgba(250,246,240,0.82); font-style: italic; font-weight: 400;"
          >
            &ldquo;{t.quote}&rdquo;
          </blockquote>

          <figcaption class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t" style="border-color: rgba(212,175,55,0.2);">
            <div class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #D4AF37; letter-spacing: 0.06em;">
              {t.name}
            </div>
            <div class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.28em] mt-1" style="color: rgba(250,246,240,0.45);">
              {t.event}
            </div>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
